208044.「ただいまより 第７回\n アストルティア・クイーン コンテストに\n 参加する:
We are pleased to introduce to you the
beautiful women who will be participating in
the 7th Astoltia Queen Contest!

208045.「総勢４８人の予選を勝ち抜いた 上位７名と\n ファルパパ神による特別推薦枠 １:
The top seven winners from the 48 qualifiers,
plus one specially recommended by Falpapa God,
will compete for the top eight spots!

208046.「まずは 前大会の覇者が 堂々の登場だ！\n ３回目の出場で ついに 勝ち取った:
First of all, the champion of the previous tournament made a grand entrance! This is the third time they've won the crown! Will they
ride this momentum to back-to-back championships?

208047.「みんなのズッ友は 今やクイーン！ 唯一無二の\n 濃すぎる魅力で 再び栄冠を:
Everyone's friend is now a queen! The one and only, the one and only, the one and only, the one and only, the one and only, the one and
only, the one and only, the one and only! A true, authentic, rising star! Historica!

208048.「ヒストリカ イズ ノット かませドッグ！\n もう 場違いとは 言わせない！！:
Historica is Knot, a dog with a bite! Don't
let anyone tell you you're out of place! I am
the Queen of Valentine!

208049.「キミとの友情が 結実して 手に入った\n クイーンの座を 奪おうとする者がいる:
If anyone tries to take away the title of queen that I have earned through my friendship with you, I'll take my revenge with the
Warataro v22!

208050.「幾度となく 阻まれし クイーンの座……。\n だが！ 神は その者の 器の大き:
The title of queen has been repeatedly denied
to me. But! God only grants trials that match
the size of the person's vessel.

208051.「だとすればッ！ 今まさに 対峙した\n この大いなる試練を 乗り越えられるか！:
If that's the case! Can you overcome this great trial we face right now? The battlePurineSeth Hero Princess Anlucia of
purity!

208052.「何度 傷つこうと…… 何度 涙を流そうと！\n みんなの応援という 希望があれ:
No matter how many times I get hurt, no matter
how many tears I shed! With the hope of your
support, I will rise again and again!

208053.「今年こそ クイーンの座を手にして\n 願いは 必ず かなうものだと 皆に示しま:
This year, I will be crowned queen and show
everyone that wishes do come true!

208054.「昨年 女王の座は 明け渡したが その人気は\n いまだ健在！ その澄んだ瞳に宿:
Although she vacated her throne last year, her
popularity is still strong! The innocent light
in her clear eyes is truly Heal!

208055.「彼女の行く先には いつも いやしの風が吹く！\n 変わらぬ笑顔で 再び ホイミ:
Wherever her goes, a healing wind always blows! With her unchanging smile, will she once again create a whirlwind of healing?
Seraphi, the blue guide!

208056.「えへへ。みんな いつも応援ありがとう！\n 今年も 精一杯がんばるから みんな:
Ehehe. Thanks for all your support! I'll do my
best this year too, so I hope you guys can
have fun with me too!

208057.「天よ 地よ！ 火よ 水よ！\n とどろけ 雷鳴！ うなれ 竜巻！！:
O heavens, earth! Fire, water! Thunder,
thunder! Rumble, tornado!

208058.「幻魔を駆り 大自然をあやつる天地雷鳴士。\n 陰と陽の ふたつの衆を代表して\:
The druid who drives the demons and manipulates nature. Asahi, the representative of the yin and yang, who shines the light of
heaven and earth, is here!

208059.「わあ こんなに 大きな舞台に立てるなんて！\n ちょっと 緊張してきちゃったけ:
Wow, I never thought I would be on such a big
stage! I'm getting a little nervous, but I
have to be prepared for this.

208061.「さらに ニューフェイスの登場です！\n エテーネ王国 王弟の妻にして 一児の母:
And now, a new face! She is the wife of the King's brother, Ethene Kingdom, and mother of one. A married woman or not, the one with the
most charm wins!

208062.「純粋に その美を競うだけなら 最強クラス！\n うるわしの聖母こそが クイーン:
If it were purely a beauty contest, she would be one of the best! Our Lady of Leap of Faith is worthy of the title of queen. Marone, the
graceful, ancient lady!

208063.「もし 私が 上位に入れたら\n 王国の人たちは 喜んでくれるかしら？\n それ:
Do you think the people of the kingdom would
be happy if I made it to the top? And her,
too.

208064.「とはいえ せっかくの機会ですので\n 勝敗は気にせずに 楽しみたいと思います。:
However, since it's an opportunity for me to enjoy myself, I'd like to enjoy it without worrying about winning or losing. I look
forward to working with you.

208065.「……続きましては このお方。\n 酸いも甘いも 飲みくだして\n 自由を愛し:
Next is this man. I have drunk the sweet and
the sour, I love freedom, and I live in
freedom!

208066.「まともに 取り合ってもらえなかったため\n 若干 むりやり お越しいただきまし:
We had to force you to come here because you
didn't take us seriously. Wagmika, the self-
defeating alchemist!

208069.「ワシに投票するようなヤツも クソだ……。\n むにゃむにゃ……。ひっく！:
And those who would vote for me are also shit.
Squishy. Hiccup!

208070.「えー。気を取り直しまして。\n 次に 紹介いたしますのは この方。\n ……裏:
Eh. Let me get back on track. Next, I would
like to introduce this gentleman. There are
those who say he is a traitor.

208071.「だが あなたは 知っているはずだ。\n 過酷な運命に立ち向かった 彼女の真実を:
But you know. The true story of her who faced
the harshest fate! ally Kamil erased from
history!

208072.「……競うべき相手に 勇者がいるとは\n 運命も 酷な悪戯をするものです。\n:
Fate has played a terrible trick on us, for we
have Hero to contend with. But then again,
this is a battlefield.

208073.「負けるわけには いきません！\n 私には この命を盾として\n 守らなければな:
I cannot lose! I have someone whose life I
must protect as a shield!

208074.「さあ いよいよ ラストのご紹介です。\n 今回 ファルパパ神の ご推薦を受けた:
Now, at last, it's time to introduce the last
one. This time, the Falpapa God recommended
this lucky girl!

208075.「引きこもり娘と あなどるなかれ。その実態は\n 皇女にして 一流技術者という:
Do not underestimate her as a recluse. In reality, she is a blessed princess and a first-class engineer. She is truly an oasis of
purity that moistens the hot sand!

208076.「その手にかかれば 運命だって 改造できそう！\n 有能なる テクニカル・プリン:
In his hands, even fate can be altered! The
talented technical PurineSeth! Princess Ulta!

208077.「ふむ この城の動力は どうなっておるのじゃ？\n 勝者となった暁には ぜひ そ:
Hmmm... how is this castle powered? I would
love to study its mechanism when we are
crowned the winners!

208078.「皆の者！ わらわは クイーンを目指す！\n ウルベア帝国の皇女に 相応しい勝利:
All of you! I seek to be queen! I ask for your
help in achieving a victory worthy of the
Princess of the Urbea Empire!

208079.「……以上 ８名の美女たちが\n クイーンの座をかけて コンテストを争います。:
These eight beauties will compete for the
title of queen.

208080.「栄光の座に かがやくのは\n 果たして 誰なのか！？\n それを決めるのは あ:
Who will be crowned with glory? It is you who
will decide!

208081.「どうですか <pc>さん。\n 今回も選りすぐりの美女が そろいました。\n:
What do you think ? We have a great selection of beauties for you to choose from this time. Did you find your favorite
one?

208082.「クイーンにふさわしいと思う 美女が決まったら\n あなたの持つ票を 投じてあげ:
If you decide on a beauty you think deserves
to be queen, cast your vote for her.

208083.「なお 投票につきましては 集計係モカの所で\n おこなっていただくことに なっ:
Voting is to be done at Tallier Mocha's
office.

208084.「票を投じましたら お話がありますので\n 私の所に お立ち寄りください。\n:
After you cast your vote, please stop by my
place for a chat. I'll be outside.

208129.「ただいまより 第７回\n アストルティア・クイーン コンテストの\n 結果発表:
We are now announcing the results of the 7th
Astoltia Queen Contest!

208130.「この ショコラフォンテヌ城の\n クイーンの座は いったい 誰の手に！？\n:
Who will be the queen of the Chocolat Fontenay
Castle? The result will finally be revealed!

208131.「皆さま！ ステージに ご注目ください！:
Ladies and gentlemen! Please pay attention to
the stage!

210798.「この勝負っ あたしが もらっちゃうよー！\n ヨイちゃんの分まで がんばるんだ:
I'll take this match! I'll do my best to make
up for Yoi-chan!
